quran[13{c,v,t}:
36,71,kya yeh log dekhte nahi hain ke hum ne apne hathon ki banai hui cheezon mein se inn ke liye maweshi peda kiye aur ab yeh un ke maalik hain
36,72,"hum ne unhen is terhan inn ke bas mein kar diya hai ke unn mein se kisi par yeh sawaar hotay hain, kisi ka yeh gosht khatay hain"
36,73,aur unn ke andar inn ke liye terhan terhan ke fawaid aur mashrobat hain phir kya yeh shukar guzaar nahi hotay ?
36,74,yeh sab kuch hotay hue unhon ne Allah ke siwa dosray khuda bana liye hain aur yeh umeed rakhtay hain ke inn ki madad ki jaye gi
36,75,woh inn ki koi madad nahi kar satke balkay yeh log ultay unn ke liye haazir baash lashkar banay hue hain
36,76,"acha, jo baatein yeh bana rahay hain woh tumhe ranjida nah karen, inn ki chhupi aur khuli sab baton ko hum jantay hain"
36,77,kya ensaan daikhta nahi hai ke hum ne usay nutfa se peda kya aur phir woh Sarih jhagralu ban kar khara ho gaya ?
36,78,"ab woh hum par misalein chaspan karta hai aur apni paidaiesh ko bhool jata hai kehta hai"" kon un hadion ko zindah kere ga jabkay yeh boseedah ho chuki hon? """
36,79,"is se kaho, aِnhin wohi zindah kere ga jis ne pehlay inhen peda kya tha, aur woh takhleeq ka har kaam jaanta hai"
36,80,wohi jis ne tumahray liye harey bharay darakht se aag peda kar di aur tum is se apne cholhe roshan karte ho
36,81,"kya woh jis ne asmano aur zameen ko peda kya iss par Qadir nahi hai ke inn jeson ko peda kar sakay? kyun nahi, jabkay woh maahir Khalaq hai"
36,82,woh to jab kisi cheez ka iradah karta hai to is ka kaam bas yeh hai ke usay hukum day ke ho ja aur woh ho jati hai
36,83,"pak hai woh jis ke haath mein har cheez ka mukammal Iqtidaar hai, aur isi ki taraf tum pulta-ay jaane walay"
